Allow official AI extension hosts to use Node's global navigator

Node 21+ exposes navigator globally. The Codex extension opts into that
behavior, so keep the VS Code migration guard from turning a valid extension
host launch into PendingMigrationError when Jack has explicitly enabled the
compatibility runtime.

Index: code-server/lib/vscode/src/vs/workbench/api/node/extensionHostProcess.ts
